C.\\u00c2Four of the sports that were introduced during the Tokyo Olympics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 including 3\\u00c3\\u00973 basketball, surfing, sport climbing and skateboarding \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 will make a reappearance this summer.\", \"from\": 4405, \"to\": 4660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4449, \"end\": 4460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 6.65232556099783e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2028 Olympics\", \"from\": 4428, \"to\": 4445}, {\"ngram\": \"NBC.\\u00c2Four\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4484}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports\", \"from\": 4488, \"to\": 4498}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 4527, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"3\\u00c3\\u00973 basketball\", \"from\": 4560, \"to\": 4575}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4584}, {\"ngram\": \"sport climbing\", \"from\": 4586, \"to\": 4600}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 4619, \"to\": 4622}, {\"ngram\": \"a reappearance\", \"from\": 4633, \"to\": 4647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the height of the Olympic action \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 and some of the most popular events, like swimming and gymnastics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 will transpire in central Paris, many other sports will take further afield.\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4801, \"end\": 4806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.249754493796806e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the height\", \"from\": 4668, \"to\": 4678}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic action\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4700}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 4701, \"to\": 4704}, {\"ngram\": \"the most popular events\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4740}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming and gymnastics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 4747, \"to\": 4774}, {\"ngram\": \"many other sports\", \"from\": 4808, \"to\": 4825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Roucas-Blanc Marina in the coastal city of Marseille, located in the south of France, will serve as a home base for the sailing competition.\\u00c2According to the Olympic website,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthe quality of the water conditions off the coast of Marseille, with relatively constant winds and a coastal configuration that is correctly oriented in relation to the dominant winds, without any currents or tides, will ensure ideal tactical and strategic conditions for the competitors.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d \\u00c2 Soccer matches will also be held in Marseille at the Stade V\\u00c3\\u00a9lodrome arena and at various stadiums in Bordeaux, Saint-\\u00c3\\u0089tienne, Lyon, Nantes and Nice,as noted by CNN The surfing competition will not even take place in the same hemisphere.\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 5569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4899, \"end\": 4908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.999999999659849, \"rank\": 3.3983105184020687e-10, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 4934, \"end\": 4940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999976753315, \"rank\": 2.2644203464820203e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5086, \"end\": 5095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.999999999659849, \"rank\": 3.3983105184020687e-10, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/